claim: Flublok contains 45 micrograms (mcg) of HA per strain vs 15 mcg of HA per strain in a standard-dose influenza vaccine.
explanation: A table listing solicited local and systemic adverse event rates (%) for Flublok (N=2272) versus placebo (N=2231), showing percentages of any, moderate, and severe events for categories such as pain, redness, headache, fatigue, etc. The table presents adverse event rates and does not provide any information on HA content per strain, so it does not support the claim
